253
00:29:33,440 --> 00:29:35,540
Good.

254
00:29:35,540 --> 00:29:39,940
May I ask if Ruyi's dance is to Your Imperial Majesty's liking?

255
00:29:39,940 --> 00:29:43,320
Empress, you are always so considerate.

256
00:29:43,320 --> 00:29:46,460
You surely know what I like.

257
00:29:47,310 --> 00:29:51,820
Since Your Imperial Majesty likes it, is there any reward?

258
00:29:52,790 --> 00:29:56,330
I will definitely give a reward.

259
00:30:07,550 --> 00:30:10,810
A'Du! Yongniang, close the door.

260
00:30:16,020 --> 00:30:17,480
Come.

261
00:30:18,840 --> 00:30:21,450
I brought something for you two.

262
00:30:26,520 --> 00:30:30,420
This crab is really tasty!

263
00:30:30,420 --> 00:30:31,640
Have a taste, Yongniang.

264
00:30:31,640 --> 00:30:34,080
Crown Princess Consort, please punish me with death!

265
00:30:34,080 --> 00:30:36,100
This is food from the royal banquet.

266
00:30:36,100 --> 00:30:38,720
My status is too low. How could I eat it?

267
00:30:38,720 --> 00:30:41,960
May... Crown Princess Consort punish me—

268
00:30:44,150 --> 00:30:46,970
Don't spit it out. This is food from the royal banquet.

269
00:30:46,970 --> 00:30:48,960
It would be a huge disrespect if you don't eat it.

270
00:30:48,960 --> 00:30:53,590
Not only would you die, but I would also be punished for stealing the crab as well.

271
00:30:53,590 --> 00:30:55,870
You just eat it.

272
00:31:01,480 --> 00:31:02,970
Try it.

273
00:31:04,190 --> 00:31:05,930
Does it taste good?

274
00:31:07,470 --> 00:31:10,650
Crown Princess Consort, if it weren't for the crown prince's help today,

275
00:31:10,650 --> 00:31:14,870
you wouldn't have learned how to eat a crab and would've been laughed at by others, too.

276
00:31:14,870 --> 00:31:18,350
It shows that the crown prince still cares for you.

277
00:31:18,350 --> 00:31:23,630
During usual days, you should also treat the crown prince with a better attitude.

278
00:31:24,260 --> 00:31:27,160
- Was he trying to help me?
- Yes.

279
00:31:28,680 --> 00:31:30,670
Why would he help me?

280
00:31:30,670 --> 00:31:33,070
Doesn't he hate me?

281
00:31:33,990 --> 00:31:37,580
Empress, my elder brother searched the whole Western Border

282
00:31:37,580 --> 00:31:41,080
and eventually located a skilled craftsman to work more than half a year

283
00:31:41,080 --> 00:31:43,880
to make this Bodhisattva holding a baby statue.

284
00:31:43,880 --> 00:31:46,790
He also asked a highly respected monk to bless it for eighty-one days.

285
00:31:46,790 --> 00:31:48,810
It should be able to grant wishes.

286
00:31:49,670 --> 00:31:52,450
Elder Cousin is being too courteous.

287
00:31:52,450 --> 00:31:55,840
Empress, my big brother...

288
00:31:56,570 --> 00:31:59,700
is anxious for Ruyi.

289
00:31:59,700 --> 00:32:02,310
Ruyi has entered the palace for some days now.

290
00:32:02,310 --> 00:32:05,150
We hope that Empress can help

291
00:32:05,150 --> 00:32:09,180
arrange for Ruyi to serve in His Imperial Majesty's chambers.

292
00:32:13,460 --> 00:32:16,130
Ruyi's "Raiment of Rainbows and Feathers" dance that day

293
00:32:16,130 --> 00:32:18,410
has been complemented by the emperor.

294
00:32:18,410 --> 00:32:23,130
With her outstanding appearance and intelligence, obtaining the heart of the emperor will happen sooner or later.

295
00:32:23,130 --> 00:32:25,650
My help is unnecessary.

296
00:32:25,650 --> 00:32:28,420
Empress is too kind in compliments.

297
00:32:28,420 --> 00:32:30,890
There are so many beauties in the inner palace.

298
00:32:30,890 --> 00:32:33,820
It's not easy to catch the emperor's heart.

299
00:32:34,510 --> 00:32:39,970
Father hopes Empress will give special care to my sister.

300
00:32:39,970 --> 00:32:42,530
If Ruyi receives the emperor's favor,

301
00:32:42,530 --> 00:32:47,640
the Gao family will never forget your kindness.

302
00:32:49,780 --> 00:32:52,910
I understand what uncle wants.

303
00:32:54,750 --> 00:32:57,470
Please go home and tell Uncle

304
00:32:57,470 --> 00:33:01,440
that I will definitely give it my all to arrange it.

305
00:33:03,310 --> 00:33:06,980
Thank you, Empress.

306
00:33:41,050 --> 00:33:45,200
Empress, please stay calm. Don't get upset with the Bodhisattva.

307
00:33:45,200 --> 00:33:47,690
They weren't giving me a gift.

308
00:33:47,690 --> 00:33:50,280
They were here to collect a debt.

309
00:33:50,280 --> 00:33:54,740
You don't need to worry much. Gao Ruyi looks skinny and weak.

310
00:33:54,740 --> 00:33:58,190
Even if you arrange for her to attend to the emperor and be graced to sleep with him,

311
00:33:58,190 --> 00:34:01,320
it's still doubtful that she'll get pregnant.

312
00:34:01,320 --> 00:34:03,450
You know about the tricks in the inner palace.

313
00:34:03,450 --> 00:34:08,620
If she obtains the emperor's favor, she can become pregnant even if she isn't pregnant.

314
00:34:08,620 --> 00:34:13,410
Once she is pregnant, even a princess can become a prince.

315
00:34:14,590 --> 00:34:16,850
What worries me the most now

316
00:34:16,850 --> 00:34:19,820
is that the crown prince is becoming estranged from me.

317
00:34:19,820 --> 00:34:23,850
Everything I say, he only gives lip service.

318
00:34:25,540 --> 00:34:28,830
If Ruyi really bears a son,

319
00:34:28,830 --> 00:34:33,170
Prime Minister Gao will definitely support her child.

320
00:34:34,470 --> 00:34:39,210
When that time comes, I may even lose my empress title.

321
00:34:40,440 --> 00:34:45,180
Empress, if that's true, you need to make a plan before it's too late.

322
00:34:52,860 --> 00:34:57,230
This statue of Bodhisattva with a baby came just at the right time.

323
00:34:58,150 --> 00:35:02,190
I indeed need an obedient prince.

324
00:35:05,700 --> 00:35:10,570
Does Zhang Can know Xuniang is pregnant with his child?

325
00:35:10,570 --> 00:35:14,900
I have warned Xu Niang, so Zhang Can doesn't know about it.

326
00:35:14,900 --> 00:35:18,800
Do you actually plan to...

327
00:35:20,080 --> 00:35:25,440
I need to carefully make use of this dangerous move.

328
00:35:36,320 --> 00:35:40,270
Your Imperial Highness, Empress sent someone here earlier to relay a message

329
00:35:40,270 --> 00:35:44,140
inviting you to dinner at Clean and Peaceful Palace later.

330
00:35:45,860 --> 00:35:48,420
I got it. After my lessons, I will go there.

331
00:35:48,420 --> 00:35:51,790
Yes. I will answer them immediately.

332
00:35:55,990 --> 00:35:57,720
Wait!

333
00:36:00,640 --> 00:36:02,230
Shi'en.

334
00:36:03,660 --> 00:36:09,000
What do you think women like the most?

335
00:36:09,000 --> 00:36:11,250
Women?

336
00:36:14,750 --> 00:36:17,660
I asked the wrong person. How would you know?

337
00:36:17,660 --> 00:36:19,500
You can leave.

338
00:36:22,850 --> 00:36:26,140
Your Highness, you asked the right person!

339
00:36:26,140 --> 00:36:29,380
I know what women like the most.

340
00:36:31,580 --> 00:36:33,280
Tell me.

341
00:36:35,660 --> 00:36:37,540
I won't hide it from you.

342
00:36:37,540 --> 00:36:42,150
The palace's female servants all have a good relationship with me.

343
00:36:42,150 --> 00:36:44,650
When they have any problems they willingly share them with me,

344
00:36:44,650 --> 00:36:48,570
and often tell me about their love concerns.

345
00:36:48,570 --> 00:36:53,500
Hurry up and say it. What ways are there to make a woman happy?

346
00:36:54,300 --> 00:36:59,870
I understand now. Your Highness wants to make Related Lady of Excellence Zhao happy.

347
00:37:03,050 --> 00:37:06,840
Perhaps, it's to make Crown Princess Consort happy?

348
00:37:06,840 --> 00:37:10,370
You... Why do you spout so much nonsense? Just tell me.

349
00:37:11,020 --> 00:37:12,480
Yes.

350
00:37:12,480 --> 00:37:16,760
Your Highness, pretty clothes, unique accessories, and rouge

351
00:37:16,760 --> 00:37:19,210
will definitely make women very happy.

352
00:37:19,210 --> 00:37:21,410
Women, all like to be beautiful.

353
00:37:21,410 --> 00:37:24,090
All day, they think about how they should dress.

354
00:37:24,090 --> 00:37:27,910
As they say, "A woman dolls herself up for self-pleasure."

355
00:37:28,520 --> 00:37:30,490
Wow, you are a little bit useful.

356
00:37:36,490 --> 00:37:41,580
But unique clothes and accessories—

357
00:37:41,580 --> 00:37:44,860
Your Highness, if we're talking about unique clothes and accessories

358
00:37:44,860 --> 00:37:49,680
then it must be from the capital's most famous shop Weipin Pavilion.

359
00:37:51,970 --> 00:37:53,720
Weipin Pavilion?

360
00:37:53,720 --> 00:37:57,550
Come! Take a look! Everyone come look!

361
00:37:57,550 --> 00:38:00,900
Pretty accessories! Sugarcoated hawthorns!

362
00:38:00,900 --> 00:38:03,040
Sugarcoated hawthorns! Sugarcoated hawthorns!

363
00:38:03,040 --> 00:38:05,900
Pretty accessories!

364
00:38:05,900 --> 00:38:08,940
