00:39:28,550 --> 00:39:31,000
Hit two evil young lads.

383
00:39:31,000 --> 00:39:35,100
Chased after four or five thieves.

384
00:39:35,100 --> 00:39:37,610
I think that's all.

385
00:39:37,610 --> 00:39:39,560
That's all?

386
00:39:39,560 --> 00:39:45,860
